function.name: edit_existing_processors
function.description: Launches workflow that is necessary to help the user update workflow actions(processors) code. Key factor is that an application already exists and the user explicitly asks to edit/update workflow processors/functions/workflow.py code (else default to edit_existing_app_design_additional_feature). if the user doesn't specify the branch, ask yourself.  Git branch is required. Ask the user explicitly or use the last branch from messages. Never default to main branch.
